# NETWEB: Windows reserved device names (cannot exist on NTFS — any case, any extension)
# https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/fileio/naming-a-file
[Aa][Uu][Xx]
[Aa][Uu][Xx].*
[Cc][Oo][Nn]
[Cc][Oo][Nn].*
[Nn][Uu][Ll]
[Nn][Uu][Ll].*
[Pp][Rr][Nn]
[Pp][Rr][Nn].*
[Cc][Oo][Mm][0-9]
[Cc][Oo][Mm][0-9].*
[Ll][Pp][Tt][0-9]
[Ll][Pp][Tt][0-9].*

